<description>
<![CDATA[It’s my bday, and as I say every year, it’s another trip around the Sun.  So much has happened in 365 days and I’ve been busier than ever, sometimes overwhelmingly so. I started a podcast, wrote a second book through a publisher (available next year), started school (again), worked on new screenplays, attended countless premiers/ events, booked roles, and grew my audience… but I also burned out, dealt with depression, went through heartbreak, and still sometimes felt directionless in life.  Yet, through the ups and downs, I’m very grateful for this life. Even if it wasn’t the way I originally imagined, it ended up even better. Thank you all for being here 💫<br>#birthdaygirl
